\alias{rviber}
\docType{package}
\title{rviber: AI Vibe Coder for RStudio}
\description{
An AI-powered coding assistant that lives inside RStudio.
Supports Groq, Gemini, OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, Mistral, and any
OpenAI-compatible provider. Chat with AI about your code, generate R
scripts from plain English, fix errors, explain selected code, autocomplete
the next lines, run and debug code, and generate ggplot2 charts.
}
\author{
